  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A line of spiraling black chakra 60 feet long and 5 feet wide emanates from you in a direction you choose. Each creature in range must make a Charisma saving throw. On a failed save, creatures take 4d8 Necrotic damage and gain 1 rank of Concussed as they begin to rapidly age and revert back to their normal age suffering shock, or half as much damage on a pass.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and damage by 2d8.</p>",
